sentence.text: Correct classification of HGSC may have potential impcoenzyme A biosynthetic processs for cancer prevention and improve our understanding of ovarian serous carcinogenesis

Methods: The fallopian tubes in 58 cases of pelvic HGSC (54 cases of ovarian primary, 3 cases of tubal primary, 1 case of peritoneum) and 25 cases of pelvic non-HGSC (5 cases of ovarian low-grade serous cancer, 9 cases of endometrioid cancer, and 11 cases of clear cell ovary carcinoma) were collected from June 2015 to December 2016, and serially examined under T cell costimulation microscope (SEE-FIM protocol).
